        <item>
            <title>0.7.2</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 16:26:16 +0200</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>702</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.7.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Jarvis 0.7.2</h2>
<p><b>Telegram stability fix.</b> Fixes the crash some users hit when the Telegram
connection closed (disconnecting, reconnecting, or the engine restarting itself).
Root-caused from crash reports: Jarvis was reading from the Telegram engine while
it was shutting down internally. It now stands clear the moment a shutdown begins,
and waits out a safety window before reconnecting.</p>
]]></description>
